{"TopicId":146929,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Is KSP ever run on sale.","CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T15:58:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T15:58:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs KSP ever run on sale, what cost I can expect, and when?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T16:32:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve seen the PC version on sale through Steam and other outlets like GOG, 30-40% off is pretty typical.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T16:34:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wouldn\u0027t say \u0022all the time\u0022 but a lot. I wouldn\u0027t be surprised if there\u0027s a labor day sale this weekend.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pecan","CreatedById":96332,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T17:24:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou just missed it half-price on Steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T17:24:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s practically free anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mastikator","CreatedById":135309,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T17:26:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s easily worth full price though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pincushionman","CreatedById":98495,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-01T19:10:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve ralely seen it anything other than full-price or 40% off, for\u00A0some reason.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sharpy","CreatedById":145504,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-02T12:21:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222738421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472750776\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135309\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mastikator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Mastikator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s easily worth full price though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor PC or Mac.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot entirely so for consoles...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-02T12:26:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222739382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472818877\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sharpy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Sharpy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor PC or Mac.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot entirely so for consoles...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t speak on consoles for KSP in particular, but I can honestly say if you have a remotely decent PC and have the choice between PC an console, and you choose console, you did it to yourself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBack to the actual question, though, KSP goes on sale every few months. I personally paid full price back in 2013 and it was something like $26. I felt bad at the time when it went on sale a few days later, but really it\u0027s among the best $26 I\u0027ve ever spent.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sharpy","CreatedById":145504,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-02T12:28:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://isthereanydeal.com/#/page:game/info?plain=kerbalspaceprogram\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://isthereanydeal.com/#/page:game/info?plain=kerbalspaceprogram\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://isthereanydeal.com/#/page:game/price?plain=kerbalspaceprogram\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://isthereanydeal.com/#/page:game/price?plain=kerbalspaceprogram\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRegister and click \u0022Wait for better price\u0022, to get a notification about sales.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-02T12:30:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222739382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472818877\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sharpy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Sharpy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor PC or Mac.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot entirely so for consoles...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt will be. Give Squad time and they will fix it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut let\u0027s not get into this. There\u0027s another thread for console moaning, so only happy faces here \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T00:37:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI an not interested in console. I found a free download of 0.25 (The copyright expired) and really like it. I would like the latest version but $40 is almost too much.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pincushionman","CreatedById":98495,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T01:54:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222740176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472863051\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brent Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Brent Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u2026\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EI found a free download of 0.25 (\u003C/span\u003EThe copyright expired)\u2026\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EI can assure you that the copyright has not expired.\u003C/b\u003E You can, however, download versions up to 0.13.3 for free.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/131906-the-earliest-versions-of-kerbal-space-program/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T03:53:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn most countries the copyrights will not expire until everyone here is long dead. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf Disney continues to have it\u0027s way, in the US it won\u0027t ever expire.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKeep waiting on the sale, it will come back around.\u00A0 You don\u0027t want to buy it till after the next patch anyway, its not in a very good state at the moment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-03T03:58:57Z\u0022 title=\u002209/03/2016 03:58  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Alshain\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T04:06:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe a winter sale? Checkout the SteamDB\u00A0page (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://steamdb.info/app/220200/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://steamdb.info/app/220200/\u003C/a\u003E) there\u0027s a graph at the bottom with past\u00A0discounts and duration. I paid full price in 2013 ($27 IIRC) and have played thousands of hours.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Harry Rhodan","CreatedById":119953,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T11:03:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222740176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472863051\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brent Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Brent Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(The copyright expired)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTime flies when you\u0027re having fun but I don\u0027t think the devs have been dead for 70 years now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T12:38:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222740231\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472867648\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298495\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pincushionman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, pincushionman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EI can assure you that the copyright has not expired.\u003C/b\u003E You can, however, download versions up to 0.13.3 for free.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/131906-the-earliest-versions-of-kerbal-space-program/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI says when you open it C\u00A02011 - 2014\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat!?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-03T12:38:29Z\u0022 title=\u002209/03/2016 12:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Brent Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxxQ","CreatedById":102622,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-03T13:50:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222740509\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221472906290\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brent Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Brent Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\nI says when you open it C\u00A02011 - 2014\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\nWhat!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2014 was when that version was RELEASED. \u00A0The copyright date for anything means that\u0027s the year that the copyright starts going into effect. \u00A0When there are multiple years included in the copyright (as in your example), they are there to cover previous versions - i.e. KSP was first copyrighted in 2011, and the current version includes that copyright, as well as the new version that has now been copyrighted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-08T18:20:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe older versions after 0.13.x are not expired copyright, downloading them is piracy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I have good news, KSP is on sale at the moment!\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.humblebundle.com/store/kerbal-space-program\u0022 ipsnoembed=\u0022true\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.humblebundle.com/store/kerbal-space-program\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-08T21:38:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell that site said expired, but whatever. that place has only steam and\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t do steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-08T21:51:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems to be working fine for me, sale lasts another 10 days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is a Steam key though. If you\u0027d rather get it elsewhere, keep an eye on the KSP Store and GOG.com.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxxQ","CreatedById":102622,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-08T23:47:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222747435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022146929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473371507\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems to be working fine for me, sale lasts another 10 days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is a Steam key though. If you\u0027d rather get it elsewhere, keep an eye on the KSP Store and GOG.com.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think he meant the site where he \u0022downloaded\u0022 the \u0022expired\u0022 version of the game.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-03T16:41:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen they ran it on sale before Christmas I got it for only $13.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Fried Chicken","CreatedById":172854,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-03T22:45:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIIRC. It remains on-sale at the KSP Store thru 6-January-2017\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}